{"word":"G809 - ἀσχήμων - aschḗmōn - as-kay'-mone - Uncomely","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀσχήμων</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aschḗmōn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">as-kay'-mone</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Uncomely</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இலட்சணமில்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"deformed, indecent, unseemly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G2192 - ἔχω - échō - ekh'-o/2192\">G2192</a> (in the sense of its congener <a href=\"#/G4976 - σχῆμα - schēma - skhay'-mah/4976\">G4976</a>); properly <i>shapeless</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>inelegant:</i> - uncomely.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}